title: 152 - Memorial Weekend
description: On today's show, the boys chat about the latest news goin on in everyones life as the boys welcome in the summer with Memorial Day weekend. They jump right into the Pod Fod action as Fast 9 has been leaked on the internet. Gump and Digs begin their battle with Nick on why they should wait to go see it in theaters. The Fod includes teasers from the upcoming Rock movie, Ikea food court quality, gorillas daily, and much more from all things around the internet. Don't forget to subscribe to YouTube.com/thepodpmi and send your submissions for the folder @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you all for listening, we'll see you on Wednesday.
